profile: Catalina Faux Wood Beams supplies rustic polyurethane beams to create the look of an authentic exposed beam ceiling. Beams can be easy installed using 2x4 blocks screwed to the ceiling (either into stud or with the use of drywall anchors) then simply cap the blocks with our beams and screw into the ceiling blocks, hollow beams allow for running wire for added LED lighting. Decorate your ceilings today!
